        {
            "id": 6142055,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 品安(8088)股價拉至漲停，漲停價33.2元，成交7,767張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>品安(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8088:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8088\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8088-TW</a>)05日11:52上漲3元，股價漲停報33.2元，委買4,427,000張，成交7,767張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為記憶體模組  積體電路   快閃記憶體  代工。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>品安(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8088:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8088\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8088-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌2.58%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.07%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-257 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-210 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-47 張</li> <li>融資增減：-244 張</li> <li>融券增減：-35 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6142055",
